en together, the GPU implementation combined with\ncorrelated sampling provides a compelling computational method that will\nbroaden the application of ph-AFQMC to the description of realistic correlated\nelectronic systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2018 02:15:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-07"}
